# Intuition
<!-- Describe your first thoughts on how to solve this problem. -->
Do recursion and genrate all the possible sequences and also keep checking if open == close and when size of string becomes 2*n then push that string in answer vector.
# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
1. Recusrive 
2. Backtracking
# Complexity
- Time complexity:O(4^n)
